abstract: The 5-year-old cat, who escaped in August, was found just about where he had been lost.
snippet: The 5-year-old cat, who escaped in August, was found just about where he had been lost.
lead_paragraph: Jack the Cat did not patronize the duty-free shops. He was never spotted near any of the drinking establishments. And if he bothered to sample the food court fare, his emaciated condition would register as a scathing critique.

headline.main: Missing No More: Jack the Cat Turns Up at J.F.K.
